                    id="image_rnr_jn4_nlb">
                    <alt>Tier Match Parameters</alt>
                </image>
            </fig>
           <p>Tier match is performed on two tiers identified as <b>Tier 1</b> and <b>Tier 2</b> in
                the form. (The default values are 'IPA Target' and 'IPA Actual' respectively.) Use
                the provided radio buttons to select tiers or enter a custom tier name in the
                provided text field. You may also choose options for case sensitivy and diacritics
                when comparing tier values.</p>
        </body>
